The paper discusses a method to reduce uncertainty in neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and specifically in the subfield of deep learning. The paper proposes a new loss function to replace the SoftMax loss, which is a common loss function used in classification tasks. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
